:

*Virus* je zarazna bolest. (The virus is a contagious disease.)

Lekari su ustanovili da je *virus* uzročnik bolesti. (The doctors established that the virus is the cause of the disease.) 

Mnogi *virusi* mogu da budu opasni. (Many viruses can be dangerous.)

Neki *virusi* su veoma otporni. (Some viruses are very resistant.)